Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:08.94,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the short cherry blossom season,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:14.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rain that had washed away the flowers was clearing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:23.79,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling, Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.48,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Cabbage's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone off for his wrestling job,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:33.26,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so take some time off and think about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:41.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:45.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a poor prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:54.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been fighting on your own your entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:05.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:08.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so... don't just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Noboru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:20.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so concerned about other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take after Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:25.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that man the MP's shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:40.14,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro's teachings are in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:52.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd, Turtle's still not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.28,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was gonna come around in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:19.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I never knew Turtle lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:24.76,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru never told you guys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.43,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Turtle, I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.09,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.28,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Noboru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.28,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:50.79,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, I'll take him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:55.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:56.96,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:00.30,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was having difficulty breathing due to his fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:04.88,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I gave him something for his temperature, so he should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:10.07,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play it safe, though, and keep him here for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.44,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.51,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really... just a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:30.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, don't worry me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:37.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back on my feet once I eat something tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.84,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:44.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut up an apple for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.97,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.85,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.81,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:56.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do a thorough check up in such a small hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:00.90,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be really sure unless\N he's examined at a larger place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:13.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:17.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about what you should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.08,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling blue isn't going to get me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just back to square one, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too bad if I put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:36.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working my way up with this body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.97,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:43.28,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:54.01,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you going to do with the money you secretly took from the general?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:59.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it wasn't for anything grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:04.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd start my own little store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:10.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My very own castle, and a life independent of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a small dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much would it take...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for your little dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.51,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:33.19,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.91,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mario?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:49.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:54.47,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Turtle... really have just a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.44,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't that what the doctor said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario, what are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something about Noboru I don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,survived an atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this could be an after effect of the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.70,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:25.16,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... he needs to be examined at a bigger hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:32.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the money or the connections to get him admitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:38.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell me, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.23,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:54.81,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... do anything for Turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.81,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.14,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"No one cares for his friends like Turtle does."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:11.14,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"His kindness comes from the unmatched horrors of his past."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:16.47,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario felt frustrated that he was unable to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.88,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,and that an unknown threat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was making him powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.73,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mr. Maeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to take your temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to take Noboru to a bigger hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:46.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.98,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, why are we at the U.S. base?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:04.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario, America built the atomic bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:11.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're also the ones with the latest medical technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:17.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best place to get Noboru checked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.12,RAINBOW Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Cafe Mironga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my entire life's saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.36,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give my body and the money as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:37.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do whatever you want with me, including slave labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:42.26,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, please, lend me some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.81,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:58.81,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only lend up to 3,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.46,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:13.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you give me permission to start a business like yours with my 100,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to start a One Percent Loan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:21.58,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lend out 100,000 yen, I'll get 1,000 yen in interest every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:25.81,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 30,000 yen in a month, and in two months, 130,000 yen will become 169,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:31.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to start any business you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:37.69,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to stop you, so do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.16,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:48.20,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to tag along with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:53.32,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to teach you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.88,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, why are we at a public bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.93,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and get over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:19.44,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no sin to wash an old man's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.71,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used to serve under my patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:12.63,RAINBOW Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach them a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:16.38,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:20.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't listen to anything we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.20,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.72,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.04,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:35.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, let's find a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.55,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:07.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that boxer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.78,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, from that match!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he'll ask them to take a look at Turtle{Noboru}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.21,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.15,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:14:01.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, did he say he wants to box with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:04.48,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he said that's the condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:17.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario... but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.65,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.68,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:51.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll examine him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.87,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.25,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go tell him right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're greatly obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.11,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Jeffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.56,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People smile when they borrow money,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:54.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but their smiles become frowns when they return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:58.83,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When people borrow money, they thank you endlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:03.54,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when they have to return it,\N they glare at you like you're a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:11.94,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you wash my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:21.06,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got that scar right when I started the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:25.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scar, and this scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.71,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the scars you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are from people to whom I've lent money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:36.90,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,, in the ten years that I've been running this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:52.42,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lend money to the wrong person,\N you'll lose your life as well as your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:59.39,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want to start a moneylending business?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:11.14,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Sugi used his own scars to show me the dark side of the business."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:16.34,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"In this world, not everyone returns favors gratefully."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.75,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"This isn't a business for an ordinary person."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:27.17,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's a business for someone reckless, like me."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.72,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle thought to himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:36.70,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"How many 'medals' will end up on my body?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:48.18,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back at the café, you said you'd give your body as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.44,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:53.94,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:19:00.95,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to ask you for a little favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:08.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get this man to repay his debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.41,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:12.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes well, I'll lend you 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:22.22,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you aren't careful,\N you'll end up with as many scars as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.13,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still willing to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.68,RAINBOW Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Setagaya, Block 4, 3rd District of Mishuku, Corp Nishimura Room 205
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.74,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.44,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get that 300,000 yen ready for my return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.57,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.99,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need such a large sum of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:48.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women? Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:52.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.05,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.63,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:03.60,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we checked on him this morning, he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:09.02,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is he doing in his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.49,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.34,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for him, Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.96,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Igarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in there, Mr. Igarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.64,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.58,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you if you're trying to rob me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.37,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here from Mr. Sugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.29,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.67,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that old moneylending guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.53,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:39.30,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:51.17,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, this isn't just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:55.33,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my chance to take a step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.37,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"If I just sit around, nothing will change."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.97,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"I need to use my mind and body to take a first step."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:10.21,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,"If I don't find happiness, my life has no meaning."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:16.76,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro's teachings gave Turtle a push forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:24.44,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}sameta manazashi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:24.44,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}With my empty eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.78,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}nani wo mitsuzukeru no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.78,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}what can I\Ncontinue to watch over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:36.36,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}mamoru beki mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:36.36,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I can even sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:41.12,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}kono mi sae oshiku wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:41.12,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}my life for those\Nwhom I must protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:45.46,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Even if I rot away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.68,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Just keep on praying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:53.26,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}So far away, but\NI never give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:59.78,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ima tokenai kizuna ga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:59.78,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Our unbreakable bond {I= pretty liberal edit since it's more personalised}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.99,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}unmei to kousaku shite yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.99,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}has begun to entwine with fate;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:12.54,RAINBOW ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}kagirinai mirai e tsuzuiteyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:12.54,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}guiding us to an endless\Nfuture that's laid out before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:21.48,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}And I will get over it, it's now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:26.14,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}{walk}a far-off distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:32.37,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Feelings intertwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:36.75,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lily feels kindness for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.61,RAINBOW Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and she makes a choice.
